Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.32,0:00:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.91,0:00:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有证人在场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.29,0:00:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是... 不认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.75,0:00:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都说到这种地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.72,0:00:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 这张卡片放在了比我原来埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.63,0:00:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学为什么要选她做妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.46,0:00:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样没什么特点的平凡学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她与祥子同学一点也不相衬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.06,0:01:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.62,0:01:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越与身同高的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.09,0:01:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.71,0:01:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让裙子的摺痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.53,0:01:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让白色的水手服领结外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.71,0:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒缓的行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}红色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早醒来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最先浮现在脑中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是“今天是情人节”这个事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.24,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 鹈泽美冬从高中开始进入了莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 与其它的外部应试者稍微有点不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 我曾在莉莉安的幼儿园上过一阵学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时起 祥子同学对我来说就已经是一种特殊的存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 友子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.32,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学拥有着与他人不同的某种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.29,0:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可说是天生而来的 某种令人难以接近的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.72,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是绘画 还是跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学都不会输给任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.44,0:04:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳得真好 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.68,0:04:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使受到夸奖 她也并未与其它人变得更亲近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.41,0:04:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓小孩子 就是会对拥有与自已不同气质的人而感到敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于同班同学所投射过来的惊奇的目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.67,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学毫不在意地只以沉郁的表情无视掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学在无言地战斗着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.90,0:05:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为同班同学某句无心的话 她开始换乘班车来上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是让车送到离自已家最近的候车点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再从那里乘上班车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了这种费劲的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而平凡的我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不可遏制地追寻着\N那样的祥子同学在平常的点点滴滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那份幸福并未持续多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在父亲的调职决定后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也即将离开莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就不能再看到祥子同学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.31,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我 也并非是觉得与祥子同学分别很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.33,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因无法再看到祥子同学\n而感觉到深深的遗憾而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.13,0:06:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～ 是血 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快叫老师来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.98,0:06:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.87,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在干什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为不听老师的嘱咐才会受到惩罚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.94,0:06:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了在从秋千上跌下来前\N所看到的祥子同学那不愉快的表情的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为站着荡秋千是被规章所禁止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给你了 我另外多带了一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与祥子同学的对话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从别人那里得到什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久 到了我离开幼儿园的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了送给你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 妈妈叫我要送还给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外还有这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.31,0:07:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈说这是谢礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.56,0:07:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请替我向美冬的妈妈说声谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.36,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我第一次从祥子同学\n的嘴里听到自已名字的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.27,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.92,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是永别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再回到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会再回到她的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年后 我回到了莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大后的祥子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.54,0:08:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是如同圣母玛莉亚一般优雅而恬静的女性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我急切地期盼着再会的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.95,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在哪里见过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学 老师在叫你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能暂时失陪一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.62,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻 我充份地明白了人不是那么容易改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她仍旧是全身洋盈着让他人无法接近的威严感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样毫无特点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连印象也没法让她留下的平凡的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.01,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与她之间的距离感与十年前完全没有变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是众多的同班同学中的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.78,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久 她成了红蔷薇的花蕾的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了离我更远的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.88,0:09:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样 我也因回到了\N能注视着祥子同学的生活而感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年能交给她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概还是交不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为去年的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁的巧克力也没有接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.22,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我不能接受这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我没有接受的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有接受的理由也许就能让她接受了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.23,0:10:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了今天的寻宝活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要去将卡片藏在某处！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我压抑不住自已的好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.83,0:11:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 祥子同学的红色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花蕾们到底把卡片藏在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是蔷薇馆最可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不会找到祥子同学的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的卡片就像是一张王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要怎么使用全看我的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.77,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是今天的值日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.47,0:11:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大森老师不是说过\N“立刻来理科准备室取第五节课要用的资料”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.11,0:11:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我帮忙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一点儿资料我一个人就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就拜讬你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.69,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到祥子同学的脸后 我变得害怕起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.13,0:12:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把偷偷先找到的卡片\n若无其事地拿到蔷薇馆去的胆量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在放回去的话 还来得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 好不容易才到手的卡片却...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.55,0:12:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红 白 黄的卡片将分别藏在校内的某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制时间是一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到卡片后 请带回到作为本部的蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.08,0:12:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着就可获赠\N作为附加奖的与花蕾们的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我犹豫的时候 寻宝活动开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢啊 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.86,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为想要的东西就摆在眼前 竟未做多想就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.06,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 终于理解到自已所做所为的严重性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须把它放回原来的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.17,0:13:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 即使还了回去 像这种地方一定不会有人来找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.76,0:13:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即便如此 我也没资格就这样拿着它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.95,0:13:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要祥子同学回头看看我而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为不听老师的嘱咐才会受到惩罚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是受到惩罚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.09,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与这张红色卡片一起 被关在了这个古旧的温室里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 好像吓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是来这里找卡片吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.72,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福泽佑巳同学 是祥子同学所选的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.79,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 祥子同学将隐藏的地点告诉了佑巳同学呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话 我也能稍微安心一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.45,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那些一无所知地寻找祥子同学卡片的人来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学跟我一样罪孽深重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是狗一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.28,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 像这样拼命地 干劲十足地掘着土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说佑巳同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.23,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想卡片应该就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么认真的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学果然是靠自已的力量找到这里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话 请用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么挖也无法在那里找到卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.89,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但越是把这一结局往后拖延\n我就越觉得自已变得污秽似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法再忍耐着看下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那里没有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我说晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我刚才也挖掘过那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会认为卡片在那里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.71,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然事前没有被告知过 那么佑巳同学是怎么找到这里来的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.74,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个蔷薇就叫做红蔷薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是红蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同祥子同学的分身般的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以祥子同学才会将卡片藏在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.21,0:15:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 只有佑巳同学察觉到了这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全地输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.50,0:16:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明如此的接近 我却完全未察觉到这种花的含义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到4点40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.88,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加活动的同学们请立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动结束了 请立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就在这里分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学为什么会选择她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她与祥子同学一点也不相衬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我擅自地那样认定着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但通过今天的事我明白了一些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.79,0:16:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学拥有着我所没有的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而祥子同学发现了这些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学的确有看人的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到“中”的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.83,0:17:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会无一例外地获赠与我的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.75,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是 那个 这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.67,0:17:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.49,0:17:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个... 那么这周的周日如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你想去哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去佑巳想去的地方就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我先想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会期待着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大学入学考试做得还好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 今天的估计不大好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你反倒是相当的愉快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.79,0:18:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为托了寻宝活动的福 我的愿望实现了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.12,0:18:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是那个“在毕业之前 我想看看蔷薇馆里普通学生们喧闹的样子”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 今天是我到目前为止的人生中最好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我能去您家里拜访您吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西想交给您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.18,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.59,0:18:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把卡片藏在那么奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卡片夹在“江户的物价”什么的书间 太难明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃 生气了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种话等一会儿再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我也会去由乃的家里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 姐姐 等会儿再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也是夹心巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是特意送到家里来的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多半是惯例的手制品了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 从静那里得到了酒心巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃点暖暖身体吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐在某些地方真是有点迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.53,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让我拿了专为姐姐而做的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人会是一种什么心情呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 又给我上了一堂课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得很自大的样子真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.85,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有一个懂事的妹妹我真是幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能轻松坦然地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.72,0:20:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 请不要这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果姐姐不在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了春天 志摩子也会成为二年级生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新生入学后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再察觉时 我的离开也就变得很平常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不觉得会是那么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大理石花纹巧克力蛋糕 真是非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 有关本周日的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 能请你先回教室吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.15,0:21:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 祥子同学的缝纫箱就先放在我这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜讬你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我会先放在祥子同学的桌上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.05,0:21:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.99,0:21:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟姐姐慢慢地谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 周日的事是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.17,0:21:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没有发觉是我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 美冬同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个发型很适合你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.11,0:21:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.66,0:22:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我已能坦诚地为祥子同学\N有了一个很棒的妹妹这件事而高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是发型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.40,0:22:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我内心的深处 也正在发生细微的变化
